id: pmc-dcji
title: "pm install npm:pm-changelog fails due to missing SDK dependency (upstream pm-cli#53)"
description: "When users install pm-changelog via pm install npm:pm-changelog, the extension fails to load with extension_load_failed_sdk_dependency_missing. pm-cli does not install node_modules for npm-backed extensions so @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk is unresolvable."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 0
tags[4]: install,pm-cli,sdk,upstream
created_at: "2026-05-24T06:49:25.474Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T06:55:36.140Z"
deadline: "2026-05-31T00:00:00.000Z"
assignee: steve
author: steve
estimated_minutes: 0
acceptance_criteria: "pm-cli fixes npm install to provide SDK dependency resolution or documents a workaround. pm install npm:pm-changelog works from a clean temp project without warnings."
reviewer: steve
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: 2026-05-production
release: pending-pm-cli-fix
reporter: steve
severity: high
environment: clean temp project with pm-cli@2026.5.18
repro_steps: "cd into mktemp dir, pm init, pm install npm:pm-changelog --project, pm package doctor --project"
expected_result: "pm install npm:pm-changelog loads extension and changelog command is available"
actual_result: "extension_load_failed_sdk_dependency_missing:pm-changelog - @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk import fails"
component: pm-extension-install
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
